text: Heliophanus tenuitas is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2011 in Zimbabwe. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Fauna of Zimbabwe Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Spiders described in 2011 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
